          },
          "reviewBody": "Class of 2009.\nI still remember my entrance exams were during the School Fete of 2006, and we ran into ex-students from the Class of 1996. They assured my parents that STPS was the best choice and said, \"He will go in a boy and come out a man\".\n\nIt could not be more accurate. Fifteen years later, his words still linger in my ears. The school has played a significant role in moulding me into the person I have become. My future kid will study here and be a proud Peterite- just like his old man!",
